Text: Yes weed got me into recovery

Author: aye-yo-buh-la-kay
Text: Lmao i understand!! I try to eat before getting high bc 1) I’m not having to rely so much on weed to make me eat and 2) it helps with “post eating anxiety” and since you’ve already eaten you won’t over eat or get the munchies. Hope i helped!
